TI  - Temporal changes in the taxonomic and functional diversity of fish communities in shallow Chinese lakes: the effects of river-lake connections and aquaculture
T2  - AQUATIC CONSERVATION-MARINE AND FRESHWATER ECOSYSTEMS
LA  - English
