TI  - Yield per recruit of the peacock bass Cichla monoculus (Spix and Agassiz, 1831) caught in Lago Grande at Manacapuru (Amazonas - Brazil)
T2  - BRAZILIAN JOURNAL OF BIOLOGY
LA  - English
