TI  - Partitioning no-take marine reserve (NTMR) and benthic habitat effects on density of small and large-bodied tropical wrasses
T2  - PLOS ONE
LA  - English
KW  - CORAL-REEF FISH
KW  - GREAT-BARRIER-REEF
