TI  - The futures of pastoralism in the Horn of Africa: pathways of growth and change
T2  - REVUE SCIENTIFIQUE ET TECHNIQUE-OFFICE INTERNATIONAL DES EPIZOOTIES
LA  - English
KW  - Commercialisation
KW  - Drought
KW  - Economics
KW  - Humanitarian
