TI  - Risk factors for return-to-estrus in primiparous Landrace × Yorkshire sows under tropical conditions: A large-scale retrospective study
T2  - VETERINARY WORLD
LA  - English
KW  - age at insemination
KW  - Landrace & times; Yorkshire
KW  - primiparous sow
KW  - reproductive management
KW  - return-to-estrus
KW  - tropical climate
