TI  - The effect of development interventions on the use of indigenous range management strategies in the Borana Lowlands in Ethiopia
T2  - LAND DEGRADATION & DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - indigenous knowledge
KW  - pastoralists
KW  - natural resource management
