TI  - Enhancing the Biological Control of Mite Species Infesting Olive Trees through Application of Predatory Mite Agistemus exsertus Gonzalez (Acari: Stigmaeidae) and Eco-Friendly Natural Compounds
T2  - PHYSIOLOGIA PLANTARUM
LA  - English
KW  - ANTIOXIDANT RESPONSES
