TI  - Dry-season irrigation and fertilisation affect the growth, reproduction, and seed traits of Plukenetia volubilis L. plants in a tropical region
T2  - JOURNAL OF HORTICULTURAL SCIENCE & BIOTECHNOLOGY
LA  - English
